siglyph
=======

siglyph is a Scala terminal UI library inspired by and partially ported from
pi-tui, part of the pi coding-agent project:

  https://github.com/earendil-works/pi/tree/main/packages/tui

The upstream pi project is licensed under the MIT License:

  Copyright (c) 2025 Mario Zechner

Where behavior, structure, naming, or tests intentionally mirror pi-tui, this
repository preserves that upstream attribution. The full siglyph license is in
LICENSE.
